        <var>...more .so files...</var>,
    ],
    includes = ["include"],
    deps = ["//third_party/X11"],
)
</code></pre>

<p>The following example comes from <code>third_party/gles/BUILD</code>.
   Third-party code often needs some <code>defines</code> and
   <code>linkopts</code>.
</p>

<pre><code class="lang-starlark">
